com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.documents.types

Interface SameTaxaTreesDocument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PluginDocument, TreeDocument, XMLSerializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EditableSameTaxaTreesDocument
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPhylogenyDocument, DefaultSameTaxaTreesDocument, DefaultTreeDocument, PhylogenyDocument

    public interface SameTaxaTreesDocument
extends TreeDocument
    A document containing a list of trees.

    All trees are have the exact same taxa and of the same rootedness. Currently this condition is not enforced in the code, but if you violate it then expect your code to fail in the future.
